data.description: ***OWNER MOTIVATED*** *** PRICE DROP*** Experience the epitome of vacation living in this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom fully furnished townhome nestled within a sought-after short-term rental community near Disney World. Boasting a spacious open-concept layout, the home features a modern kitchen, elegant dining area, and a relaxing living room with plush seating. Three beautifully appointed bedrooms ensure ample accommodation, including a master suite with an en-suite bathroom. Step outside to your private patio or enjoy the community pool, adding an extra dimension of relaxation. With its prime location near Disney World, this property offers excellent rental potential, making it the perfect investment and vacation retreat combine
